  "prompt": "How do I check my last 3 charges in Vodafone?",
  "response": "To check your last three charges on Vodafone, you can follow these steps:\n\n### Through the Vodafone App:\n1. **Open the Vodafone App** on your smartphone. If you haven't already, download it from the App Store or Google Play Store.\n2. **Log in** to your account using your credentials.\n3. Navigate to the **Billing** or **Usage** section to view your recent charges.\n\n### Through the Vodafone Website:\n1. Go to the **Vodafone website** and log in to your account.\n2. Once logged in, look for the **Billing** or **Usage** section to see your recent charges.\n\n### Via USSD Code (if available in your country):\n1. Dial the appropriate USSD code for your region (e.g., *#123#) and follow the prompts to check your balance and recent charges.\n\n### Customer Service:\nIf you cannot access the app or website, you can always call Vodafone customer service for assistance. They can provide you with details about your recent charges.\n\n### Note:\nThe exact steps might vary depending on your region and the version of the app or website. For the most accurate information, refer to Vodafone's official resources or customer support for your specific location.",
